host_templates.name: Cloud-Azure-Web-AppService

information.author: Centreon

description.value:
**Plugin pack to monitor Azure App Service service using RestAPI or AZCLI.**

Available Host template and related Services:

|Cloud-Azure-Web-AppService-custom|
|---|
|App-Usage|
|Cpu-Time|
|Data|
|File-System|
|Gc-Usage|
|Health|
|Http-Requests|
|IO-Operations|
|Memory|
|Response-Time|
|Status|

This Plugin-Pack provides a Host discovery *provider* to be used with the Host discovery module.

**Plugin-Pack pour superviser les resources Azure App Service via RestAPI ou AZCLI.**

Modèle d\'hôte disponibles et services associés:

|Cloud-Azure-Web-AppService-custom|
|---|
|App-Usage|
|Cpu-Time|
|Data|
|File-System|
|Gc-Usage|
|Health|
|Http-Requests|
|IO-Operations|
|Memory|
|Response-Time|
|Status|

Ce Plugin-Pack fournit un *provider* Host Discovery pour le module d\'auto-découverte d\'Hôtes
